name: Toucan
description:
Toucan

"Toucan" is part of The Fauna Notebook, a collection of 2D digital paintings that portray the unique gorgeousness found in Earth's fauna. 

In the background, each element is deeply connected to the toucan: equations of lift and flight; the chemical composition of a toucan's beak; its habitat; and a graph of its velocity over flight time, amongst other diagrams/formulas that associate with the portrayed animal.

8504 x 10630
